= DeepTest

DeepTest enables tests to run in multiple processes.

== Usage

In your Rakefile:

  require "rubygems"
  require "deep_test/rake_tasks"
  
  # sample DeepTest task
  DeepTest::TestTask.new "task_name" do |t|
    t.pattern = "test/**/*_test.rb"
    t.processes = 2 # optional, defaults to 2
  end

